Facebook's Settlement in ConnectU Dispute Is Ruled Valid by Appeals Court

-- B y   K a r e n   G u l l o
-- 
2011-04-11T17:29:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/facebook-s-settlement-in-connectu-dispute-is-ruled-valid-by-appeals-court.html
A Facebook Inc. settlement
to resolve claims that its founder  Mark Zuckerberg  stole the
idea for the social networking company is “valid and
enforceable,” a federal appeals court in  San Francisco  ruled
today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
